data.description: Beautifully Maintained Home in the Heart of Beaumont's West-End! Just off Major Drive, located in the Highly Sought Gladys West Addition, you'll find this Spacious 2,170 SQFT Home. Prominent Gable Ends in combination with Brick, Stone, and Shake Style Exterior Finishes give this Home its Attractively Unique Curb Appeal, which is also complimented by Landscaping and a Freshly Manicured Yard. Inside, you'll find a well-thought-out Open Floorplan featuring 4 Bedrooms, 2 Full Baths, and Formal Dining, as well as other highlights such as Raised Ceilings, Crown Molding, Granite Counter Tops, and Much More. Don't Miss the Opportunity to Own this West-End Jewel!
